snippet.title: The Last Meadow - Announcement Trailer | Discord
snippet.description:
“The Last Meadow” is available April 1 on Discord. Play it now: https://discord.com/settings/the-last-meadow

We’re thrilled to announce the launch of Discord’s brand-new in-house game studio, Big Wump Games with our first game release: The Last Meadow.

Will you answer the the call to restore this once-vibrant world from ruins? Become Wumpus and embark on an epic adventure to reach the fabled Last Meadow. 

Play The Last Meadow now through April 7, 2025 exclusively on the Discord desktop app and browser.
